ss="inner"><div class="ed-element ed-image" id="ed-458256866"><img src="/images/1024%2C662x390%2B6%2B0/12056783/museum.jpeg" alt="" srcset="/images/576%2C662x390%2B6%2B0/12056783/museum.jpeg 576w"></div><div class="ed-element ed-headline custom-theme" id="ed-458256869"><h3 class="left ">7 Days In London</h3></div><div class="ed-element ed-spacer" id="ed-458256872"><div style="height: 10px;" class="space"></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-text custom-theme" id="ed-458256875"><p id="isPasted">London, the capital of the United Kingdom, is a bustling global city steeped in history, culture, and modernity. It is one of the world's most iconic travel destinations, offering something for every type of traveler.</p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">&nbsp;</b></p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Key Highlights:</b></p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Historical Landmarks</b>: London is home to iconic sites like the Tower of London, Buckingham Palace, Westminster Abbey, and Big Ben.</p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Cultural Hub</b>: The city boasts world-class museums and galleries, including the British Museum, National Gallery, and Tate Modernâmany of which offer free entry.</p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Shopping Paradise</b>: From high-end stores in Oxford Street and Harrods to eclectic finds in Camden Market, London is a shopper's dream.</p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Entertainment</b>: The West End offers top-notch theater productions, while Soho and Southbank are vibrant areas for nightlife and dining.</p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Green Spaces:</b> Despite its urban vibe, London is home to beautiful parks like Hyde Park, Regentâs Park, and Richmond Park.</p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">&nbsp;</b></p><h3 style="margin-top:14.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;page-break-after:auto;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Day 1: Arrival and Exploring Central London</b></h3><p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Morning:</b> Arrive at Heathrow/Gatwick Airport and transfer to your hotel. Check-in and freshen up.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Afternoon:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level2 lfo1;">Visit <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Trafalgar Square</b> and the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">National Gallery</b>.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level2 lfo1;">Stroll to <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Covent Garden</b> for street performances and boutique shopping.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Evening:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level2 lfo1;">Dinner at a traditional British pub.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level2 lfo1;">Optional: Watch a West End musical.</p><p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Accommodation:</b> Central London hotels.</p><div align="center" style="text-align:center;"><hr size="2" width="100%" align="center"></div><h3 style="margin-top:14.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;page-break-after:auto;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Day 2: Iconic London Landmarks</b></h3><p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo6;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Morning:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo6;">Tour <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Buckingham Palace</b> (changing of the guard).</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo6;">Walk through <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">St. Jamesâs Park</b> to <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Westminster Abbey</b>.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo6;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Afternoon:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo6;">Visit <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Big Ben</b>, <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Houses of Parliament</b>, and <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">London Eye</b> for panoramic views.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo6;">Lunch by the River Thames.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo6;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Evening:</b> Explore <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Southbank</b> and enjoy its lively atmosphere.</p><p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo6;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Accommodation:</b> Same hotel.</p><div align="center" style="text-align:center;"><hr size="2" width="100%" align="center"></div><h3 style="margin-top:14.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;page-break-after:auto;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Day 3: Tower of London and City Highlights</b></h3><p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Morning:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;">Explore the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Tower of London</b> and view the Crown Jewels.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;">Walk along <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Tower Bridge</b>.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Afternoon:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;">Visit <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">St. Paulâs Cathedral</b>.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo3;">Stroll through the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Leadenhall Market</b> (Harry Potter filming site).</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Evening:</b> Dinner in the vibrant <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Shoreditch</b> area.</p><p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Accommodation:</b> Same hotel.</p><div align="center" style="text-align:center;"><hr size="2" width="100%" align="center"></div><h3 style="margin-top:14.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;page-break-after:auto;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Day 4: Museums and Culture</b></h3><p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Morning:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo5;">Visit the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">British Museum</b>.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo5;">Explore <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Soho</b> and grab brunch.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Afternoon:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo5;">Head to <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Hyde Park</b> and enjoy a leisurely walk or rent a paddleboat on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">The Serpentine</b>.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level2 lfo5;">Visit <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Kensington Palace</b>.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Evening:</b> Explore the upscale neighborhood of <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Notting Hill</b>.</p><p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Accommodation:</b> Same hotel.</p><div align="center" style="text-align:center;"><hr size="2" width="100%" align="center"></div><h3 style="margin-top:14.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;page-break-after:auto;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Day 5: Day Trip</b></h3><p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;">Options:</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Windsor Castle</b>: The Queenâs weekend home, about an hour from London.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Oxford</b>: Famous university city with stunning architecture.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo2;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Stonehenge and Bath</b>: Ancient stone circle and historic Roman baths.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;">Return to London in the evening.</p><p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Accommodation:</b> Same hotel.</p><div align="center" style="text-align:center;"><hr size="2" width="100%" align="center"></div><h3 style="margin-top:14.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;page-break-after:auto;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Day 6: Shopping and Markets</b></h3><p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo4;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Morning:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo4;">Shop along <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Oxford Street</b>, <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Regent Street</b>, and at <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Harrods</b> in Knightsbridge.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo4;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Afternoon:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo4;">Explore <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Camden Market</b> for unique finds and street food.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo4;">Visit <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Little Venice</b> for a peaceful canal-side stroll.</p><p style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo4;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Evening:</b> Enjoy dinner at a rooftop restaurant overlooking the city.</p><p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo4;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Accommodation:</b> Same hotel.</p><div align="center" style="text-align:center;"><hr size="2" width="100%" align="center"></div><h3 style="margin-top:14.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;page-break-after:auto;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Day 7: Departure</b></h3><p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo7;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Morning:</b></p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo7;">Free time for last-minute shopping or a visit to <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">The Shard</b> for breathtaking views.</p><p style="margin-left:72.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo7;">Optional: Explore the quirky <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Sky Garden</b>.</p><p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo7;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;">Afternoon:</b> Transfer to the airport for your departure.</p></div><div class="ed-element ed-spacer" id="ed-458256878"><div style="height: 30px;" class="space"></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-button scroll custom-theme" id="ed-458256881"><a class="button button-default button-color-default center" href="https://www.booking.dugnictravelsandexpeditions.com">Book now from 4200$</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-container flex-align-items-stretch flex-justify-content-space-between preset-text-and-background-default" id="ed-458256908"><div class="inner"><div class="ed-element ed-container full-width text-and-background-background parallax" id="ed-458256911"><div class="background"><div class="ed-element ed-image wv-bg" id="ed-458256914"><div class="background-image-holder" style="background-image: url(&quot;/images/675/12056834/Trafalga.jpeg&quot;);"></div></div></div><div class="inner" data-parallax-amount="50">&nbsp;</div></div></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-reference ed-reference-container preset-footer-heimdall-icon-left" id="ed-458256905" data-reference="444090718"><div class="inner" id="kontakt"><div class="ed-element ed-container flex-align-items-stretch flex-justify-content-center wv-boxed footer-heimdall-content wv-spacer" id="ed-444090721"><div class="inner"><div class="ed-element ed-container footer-heimdall-box" id="ed-444090724"><div class="inner"><div class="ed-element ed-icon footer-heimdal